  <Name>Healing Elixir</Name>
  <CastingTime>1 minute</CastingTime>
  <Range>Self</Range>
  <Duration>24 hours</Duration>
  <Level>1</Level>
  <Description>You create a healing elixir in a simple vial that appears in your hand. The elixir retains its potency for the duration or until it’s consumed, at which point the vial vanishes.
As an action, a creature can drink the elixir or administer it to another creature. The drinker regains 2d4 + 2 hit points.</Description>
